eam/apps/2134060/extras/Instant_Replay.gif.gif?t=1738018723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134060/extras/the_game_that_waits.png?t=1738018723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter your carefully planned commands at any speed and walk away from the controls at a moment\u2019s notice \u2013 the turn-based gameplay offers generous breathing room as you game. Gameplay doesn\u2019t require hand-eye coordination, or even the ability to hold a controller. Quarterstaff is a game accessible to gamers of all skill levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Generic Lake Monster, LLC"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134060/header.jpg?t=1738018723","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Verified for Ubuntu 12.04, Fedora 21, and Debian 8<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Pentium 4 or later that's SSE2 capable<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> MacOS 10.10 (Yosemite) or later<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Processor 64-bit<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 512 MB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257069295,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069295/movie480.mp4?t=1730179916","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257069295/movie_max.mp4?t=1730179916"},"name":"Quarterstaff Release Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steams